We see this in the
crystal lattice structure

00:02:19.940 --> 00:02:24.320 align:middle line:84%
with how the atoms or
molecules are arranged inside.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:27.260 align:middle line:84%
Marcel Vogel, a
research scientist

00:02:27.260 --> 00:02:30.770 align:middle line:84%
