00:03:23.580 --> 00:03:26.480 align:middle line:84%
In other words, our
thoughts and intent

00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:29.105 align:middle line:90%
can be amplified by the crystal.

00:03:29.105 --> 00:03:32.780 align:middle line:84%
And based on his research into
what's called ether physics,

00:03:32.780 --> 00:03:35.150 align:middle line:84%
Marcel Vogel
developed what is now

00:03:35.150 --> 00:03:38.390 align:middle line:84%
known as the Vogel-shaped
