the Earth and is very old.

00:25:27.930 --> 00:25:31.170 align:middle line:84%
So we really have all four
elements within the Earth

00:25:31.170 --> 00:25:33.610 align:middle line:90%
element of the mineral kingdom.

00:25:33.610 --> 00:25:36.540 align:middle line:84%
And we can tune in and
be aware of which element

00:25:36.540 --> 00:25:39.540 align:middle line:84%
