with primarily

00:25:39.540 --> 00:25:42.870 align:middle line:90%
as we get to know our crystals.

00:25:42.870 --> 00:25:45.960 align:middle line:84%
Once you've found a crystal
friend and brought it home,

00:25:45.960 --> 00:25:47.490 align:middle line:90%
how do you treat them?

00:25:47.490 --> 00:25:49.900 align:middle line:90%
How do you store them?

00:25:49.900 --> 00:25:54.850 align:middle line:84%
Keep in mind that crystals come
from the womb of Mother Gaia.

00:25:54.850 --> 00:25:57.280 align:middle line:84%
They're taken from
the sacred space

00:25:57.280 --> 00:25:59.410 align:middle line:90%
within the ground or a cave.

00:25:59.410 --> 00:26:04.660 align:middle line:84%
And we humans are removing them
from their natural environment.

00:26:04.660 --> 00:26:08.670 align:middle line:84%
So how do we provide a sacred
and comfortable space for them

00:26:08.670 --> 00:26:11.280 align:middle line:90%
when we bring them to our home?

00:26:11.280 --> 00:26:14.370 align:middle line:84%
This is a great
question to reflect on.

00:26:14.370 --> 00:26:16.260 align:middle line:84%
When we buy crystals
from a store,

00:26:16.260 --> 00:26:18.900 align:middle line:84%
they're usually not in
the type of environment

00:26:18.900 --> 00:26:21.070 align:middle line:90%
