00:26:21.070 --> 00:26:23.490 align:middle line:84%
We can create that
sacred space for them

00:26:23.490 --> 00:26:27.270 align:middle line:84%
when we honor them as
unique, individual beings

00:26:27.270 --> 00:26:29.200 align:middle line:90%
that they are.

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:31.550 align:middle line:84%
And what kind of
environment might a crystal

00:26:31.550 --> 00:26:33.530 align:middle line:90%
like at our home?

00:26:33.530 --> 00:26:37.040 align:middle line:84%
Well, they like to be out
so that they can be seen

00:26:37.040 --> 00:26:40.460 align:middle line:84%
and not hidden away
in a box or closet.

00:26:40.460 --> 00:26:42.470 align:middle line:84%
But if they have to
be stored, then they

00:26:42.470 --> 00:26:45.350 align:middle line:84%
