materials, like leather,

00:26:45.350 --> 00:26:47.900 align:middle line:90%
cotton, silk, or wood.

00:26:47.900 --> 00:26:49.970 align:middle line:84%
Leather is a more
insulating material,

00:26:49.970 --> 00:26:52.760 align:middle line:84%
and it will keep their
energy more quiet.

00:26:52.760 --> 00:26:54.980 align:middle line:84%
But honestly, they
prefer to be out

00:26:54.980 --> 00:26:56.630 align:middle line:90%
where they can work with us.

00:26:56.630 --> 00:26:59.570 align:middle line:84%
And if we just bring
our attention to them

00:26:59.570 --> 00:27:02.720 align:middle line:90%
to work with us, then they do.

00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:04.940 align:middle line:90%
How do they work with us?

00:27:04.940 --> 00:27:07.980 align:middle line:84%
Well, crystals can be used
to help us on all levels.

00:27:07.980 --> 00:27:11.630 align:middle line:84%
Whether it's mental, emotional,
physical, or spiritual,

00:27:11.630 --> 00:27:14.090 align:middle line:84%
all levels of our
being can be supported

00:27:14.090 --> 00:27:16.190 align:middle line:90%
by working with crystals.

00:27:16.190 --> 00:27:19.750 align:middle line:84%
They are alive and
we can talk to them.

00:27:19.750 --> 00:27:23.060 align:middle line:84%
Now remember, each
crystal is a unique being.

00:27:23.060 --> 00:27:25.670 align:middle line:84%
So hold it in your hands
and bring it near your heart

00:27:25.670 --> 00:27:27.770 align:middle line:90%
to communicate with it.

00:27:27.770 --> 00:27:31.520 align:middle line:84%
You can talk out loud or
telepathically in your mind.

00:27:31.520 --> 00:27:33.810 align:middle line:90%
Tell it what you want help with.

00:27:33.810 --> 00:27:35.660 align:middle line:84%
For example, if you
have a stomach ache,

00:27:35.660 --> 00:27:38.420 align:middle line:84%
you can let them
know and request,

00:27:38.420 --> 00:27:42.360 align:middle line:84%
please help bring me
back to homeostasis.

00:27:42.360 --> 00:27:44.040 align:middle line:84%
Once you talk to
your crystal, you

00:27:44.040 --> 00:27:47.130 align:middle line:84%
may have a sense of
how to work with it.

00:27:47.130 --> 00:27:50.370 align:middle line:84%
You may lay it on your body
or carry it in your pocket

00:27:50.370 --> 00:27:51.910 align:middle line:90%
through your day.

00:27:51.910 --> 00:27:55.730 align:middle line:84%
The key is to trust
your intuition.

00:27:55.730 --> 00:27:58.400 align:middle line:84%
When picking which
crystal to work with,

00:27:58.400 --> 00:28:00.230 align:middle line:90%
scan with your intuition.

00:28:00.230 --> 00:28:02.780 align:middle line:84%
And notice which
one speaks to you.

00:28:02.780 --> 00:28:04.460 align:middle line:90%
Trust yourself.

00:28:04.460 --> 00:28:06.800 align:middle line:90%
Don't rely on books to tell you.

00:28:06.800 --> 00:28:09.320 align:middle line:84%
This is about how you
build your relationship

00:28:09.320 --> 00:28:11.390 align:middle line:90%
with your unique crystals.

00:28:11.390 --> 00:28:13.850 align:middle line:84%
And when we build our
relationship with our crystals,

00:28:13.850 --> 00:28:17.210 align:middle line:84%
we open the door to
collaboration with the mineral

00:28:17.210 --> 00:28:18.400 align:middle line:90%
kingdom.

00:28:18.400 --> 00:28:21.560 align:middle line:84%
The mineral kingdom supports
us as powerful mediators

00:28:21.560 --> 00:28:26.936 align:middle line:84%
to bring divine energy into the
physical in a very pure way.

00:28:26.936 --> 00:28:29.450 align:middle line:84%
And one way that we
honor our crystals

00:28:29.450 --> 00:28:33.440 align:middle line:84%
is to pay attention
and care for them.

00:28:33.440 --> 00:28:35.510 align:middle line:84%
What do we need to
know to properly care

00:28:35.510 --> 00:28:37.640 align:middle line:90%
for our crystal friends?

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:40.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, one thing to keep in mind
is that they like the sunlight.

00:28:40.790 --> 00:28:43.070 align:middle line:84%
So putting them
out about at least

00:28:43.070 --> 00:28:47.000 align:middle line:84%
once a week where they can
be in the sunlight is good.

00:28:47.000 --> 00:28:49.950 align:middle line:84%
But with too much sun,
they can get dried out.

00:28:49.950 --> 00:28:53.990 align:middle line:84%
So if they're getting dry,
you can massage them with oil

00:28:53.990 --> 00:28:56.600 align:middle line:90%
to give them some moisture.

00:28:56.600 --> 00:28:58.640 align:middle line:84%
Another big aspect
of crystal care

00:28:58.640 --> 00:29:01.790 align:middle line:84%
is to regularly
cleanse your crystals.

00:29:01.790 --> 00:29:03.620 align:middle line:84%
What are some of the
most effective ways

00:29:03.620 --> 00:29:05.720 align:middle line:90%
to cleanse our crystals?

00:29:05.720 --> 00:29:08.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, since many
crystals grow from water,

00:29:08.790 --> 00:29:11.300 align:middle line:84%
one of the best and fastest
ways to cleanse them

00:29:11.300 --> 00:29:13.310 align:middle line:90%
is to give them a bath.

00:29:13.310 --> 00:29:17.690 align:middle line:84%
Use running water, like
in a fountain or a stream,

00:29:17.690 --> 00:29:20.750 align:middle line:84%
and allow for 24 hours
in this running water

00:29:20.750 --> 00:29:24.150 align:middle line:84%
to complete the
cleansing process.

00:29:24.150 --> 00:29:26.210 align:middle line:84%
Another method is to
immerse the crystals

00:29:26.210 --> 00:29:30.038 align:middle line:84%
in a bowl of sea salt
for a couple of days.

00:29:30.038 --> 00:29:32.090 align:middle line:84%
Now there are a couple
types of crystals

00:29:32.090 --> 00:29:35.550 align:middle line:84%
that don't need clearing,
because they self clear.

00:29:35.550 --> 00:29:39.660 align:middle line:84%
And these include selenite,
kyanite, and yellow calcite.

00:29:39.660 --> 00:29:42.800 align:middle line:84%
And also be aware that some of
the softer, more flaky types

00:29:42.800 --> 00:29:45.320 align:middle line:90%
of crystals dissolve in water.

00:29:45.320 --> 00:29:48.000 align:middle line:84%
Selenite, for example,
will dissolve in water.

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:52.640 align:middle line:84%
So be careful not to put these
types of crystals in the water.

00:29:52.640 --> 00:29:56.210 align:middle line:84%
And what do we do after
the crystals are cleansed?

00:29:56.210 --> 00:29:58.670 align:middle line:84%
Well, we can charge them
so that they will be fully

00:29:58.670 --> 00:30:02.090 align:middle line:90%
refreshed and full of energy.

00:30:02.090 --> 00:30:03.730 align:middle line:84%
One method for
charging our crystals

00:30:03.730 --> 00:30:08.570 align:middle line:84%
has to leave them outside for
a 24-hour period on a full moon

00:30:08.570 --> 00:30:09.640 align:middle line:90%
night.

00:30:09.640 --> 00:30:11.450 align:middle line:84%
Place them where
they can directly

00:30:11.450 --> 00:30:15.240 align:middle line:84%
take in the moonlight
and the sunlight.

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:19.250 align:middle line:84%
I also have a big amethyst
geode that's like a little cave

00:30:19.250 --> 00:30:24.320 align:middle line:84%
