inside of to charge up.

00:30:24.320 --> 00:30:26.840 align:middle line:84%
What are some other ways that
we can work with crystals

00:30:26.840 --> 00:30:29.300 align:middle line:90%
to support us in our life?

00:30:29.300 --> 00:30:33.350 align:middle line:84%
Well, we can wear them through
our day, such as on a necklace

00:30:33.350 --> 00:30:34.730 align:middle line:90%
or some kind of jewelry.

00:30:34.730 --> 00:30:37.220 align:middle line:84%
Or we can carry
them in our pocket.

