only use clear quartz.

00:34:58.500 --> 00:35:01.620 align:middle line:84%
Other types of crystals will
likely distort and cause

00:35:01.620 --> 00:35:03.090 align:middle line:90%
weird dreams.

00:35:03.090 --> 00:35:04.860 align:middle line:90%
We want our dreams to be clear.

00:35:04.860 --> 00:35:09.171 align:middle line:84%
So, only use clear quartz
for this technique.

00:35:09.171 --> 00:35:11.100 align:middle line:84%
Now having said
that, we can also

00:35:11.100 --> 00:35:15.510 align:middle line:84%
work with a certain type of
crystal called dream quartz.

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:18.210 align:middle line:84%
These crystals have a lot
of patterns and inclusions

00:35:18.210 --> 00:35:19.500 align:middle line:90%
within them.

00:35:19.500 --> 00:35:21.630 align:middle line:84%
When we look into
a dream quartz,

00:35:21.630 --> 00:35:26.580 align:middle line:84%
allow your mind to have a loose
sort of just stalled focus.

00:35:26.580 --> 00:35:29.790 align:middle line:84%
Observe without focusing
too hard on anything.

00:35:29.790 --> 00:35:35.250 align:middle line:84%
But hold a question in your mind
as you look into the crystal.

00:35:35.250 --> 00:35:38.010 align:middle line:84%
Another method is to hold
the crystal in your hand

00:35:38.010 --> 00:35:43.110 align:middle line:84%
while meditating to connect more
clearly with higher guidance.

00:35:43.110 --> 00:35:46.140 align:middle line:84%
One trick to helping us connect
to higher spiritual planes

00:35:46.140 --> 00:35:48.600 align:middle line:84%
and receive the
information more clearly

00:35:48.600 --> 00:35:51.440 align:middle line:90%
is to cool down your crystal.

00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:53.700 align:middle line:84%
Place the crystal in
the freezer for a bit

00:35:53.700 --> 00:35:58.170 align:middle line:84%
to cool it below 66 degrees
Fahrenheit or below 19 degrees

00:35:58.170 --> 00:35:59.520 align:middle line:90%
Celsius.

00:35:59.520 --> 00:36:03.690 align:middle line:84%
This helps slow down the
light as it flows through.

00:36:03.690 --> 00:36:06.180 align:middle line:84%
And it mediates the
energy so that it's easier

00:36:06.180 --> 00:36:08.480 align:middle line:90%
to connect with.

00:36:08.480 --> 00:36:11.030 align:middle line:84%
Also, it makes a
difference which hand

00:36:11.030 --> 00:36:13.460 align:middle line:90%
you're holding the crystal in.

00:36:13.460 --> 00:36:16.580 align:middle line:84%
If you want to connect with
information for the future,

00:36:16.580 --> 00:36:19.460 align:middle line:84%
then hold the crystal
in your right hand.

00:36:19.460 --> 00:36:21.920 align:middle line:84%
If you want to connect with
information about the past,

00:36:21.920 --> 00:36:24.170 align:middle line:90%
then hold it in your left hand.

00:36:24.170 --> 00:36:26.720 align:middle line:10%
Again, it's important to work
with clear quartz for this

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:29.360 align:middle line:10%
to bring the information
through with clarity

00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:32.510 align:middle line:10%
and without distortions.

